---
title: Grilled Italian Sausage and Pepper Ciabattas with Warm Marinara Dipper and Potato Wedges
description: These Italian-inspired sausage sammies are brimming with cheesy peppers and onions, piled on top of torn basil for a hit of freshness. The warm marinara is perfect for dipping those tasty wedges in!
